&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://mast-team.wdfiles.com/local--files/social-media-icons/mast-scp-wiki-staff-team.png&quot; alt=&quot;mast-scp-wiki-staff-team.png&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; /&gt; MAST Deletions workflow&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;

