any</a> - &quot;<em>There was science to be done. Lives to save.</em>&quot; Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/manymeats" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2104082&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610226523" alt="ManyMeats" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2104082)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/manymeats" >ManyMeats</a></span>.</li> </ul> <h4><span>GoI Formats</span></h4> <ul> <li><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/grant-request-for-mechacrocosquid">GRANT REQUEST FOR THE CYBERNETIC MODIFICATION OF THE CORPSE OF THE CROCOTEUTHIS GIGANTIS</a> [Prometheus Labs, Inc.] - &quot;<em>One potential new eigenweapon class which will be able to terminate an LSA is known. In this, the relevance of the second deceased LSA becomes clear.</em>&quot; Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610226523" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" >stormbreath</a></span>.</li> <li><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/adoption-poster-cupid">Adoption Poster: Cupid!</a> [Wilson's Wildlife Solutions] - &quot;<em>You told me I would be the perfect owner for Cupid because I know of nobody who wishes to meet me to do me harm. You were wrong.</em>&quot; Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/krombopulos-will" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6673645&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610226523" alt="Krombopulos_Will" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6673645)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/krombopulos-will" >Krombopulos_Will</a></span>.</li> </ul