>)</span><a href="https://aminoapps.com/c/scp-foundation/page/blog/scp-5053-anything-but-a-stick-in-the-mud/zmLN_kZSxu0wkNxd88NgG6zB6kmVZ3DQEX"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/news-09-2020/skorpt1_cr.jpg" style="width:33%;" alt="skorpt1_cr.jpg" class="image" /></a></span><span class="hover"><span style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom right, hsla(30, 25%, 50%, 0.75) 0%, hsla(30, 25%, 50%, 1) 50%);"><em>Here Be Butterflies</em></span><a href="https://aminoapps.com/c/scp-foundation/page/blog/here-be-butterflies/WMoB_2gSXuReD2knX0Yq1v4o77gMWeZwz3"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/news-09-2020/skorpt2_cr.jpg" style="width:33%;" alt="skorpt2_cr.jpg" class="image" /></a></span><span class="hover"><span style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom right, hsla(240, 25%, 50%, 0.75) 0%, hsla(240, 25%, 50%, 1) 50%);"><em>The Space Whale</em></span><a href="https://aminoapps.com/c/scp-foundation/page/blog/the-space-whale/jL1g_rYcKug5RwEz8VoRoGpbw3Kb5zknzY"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/news-09-2020/skorpt3_cr.jpg" style="width:33%;" alt="skorpt3_cr.jpg" class="image" /></a></span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></div> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <hr /> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <hr /> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <hr /> <h1><span>Q&amp;A:</span></h1> <h2><span>Q: Can I replace a blurb that you wrote for one of my articles with my own? I'm not satisfied with it.</span></h2> <p>A: Absolutely. You will always have that option at any point.</p> <h2><span>Q: I noticed an error/typo/incorrect information and wish to correct it. May I?</span></h2> <p>A: Sure! If the changes are not limited to your own article(s) and/or are substantial changes across multiple entries, you should post in that month's discussion page and then make the changes.</p> <h2><span>Q: I wrote an article and it seems to have stuck. Can I send a blurb of mine to one of the frequent collaborators?</span></h2> <p>A: Yup! It's much easier if you come to us about it, and it gives you the control over what you want shown on the news page.</p> <hr /> <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><strong>« <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/news-08-2020">August 2020</a> | <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/news-09-2020">September 2020</a></span> | <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/news-10-2020">October 2020</a> »</strong></p> </div> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <hr /> <p>by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610226524" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span></p> <div class="footnotes-footer"> <div class="title">Footnotes</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-528742-1"><a href="javascript:;" >1</a>. with a rating above 0</div> </div> 
