&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3687&quot;&gt;SCP-3687&lt;/a&gt;: Anti-Entropy Doorknobs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;A note inside of a fireproof lock-box was discovered in Mr. Hannigan&#039;s bedroom, reading: &amp;quot;Finally, I&#039;ve done it. Here, you can have this one.&amp;quot;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
