						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><strong>« <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/uau82020">August 2020</a> | <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/uau92020">September 2020</a></span> | <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/uau102020">October 2020</a> »</strong></p> </div> <hr /> <div class="feature-block"> <div class="content-panel left-column"> <div class="panel-heading"> <p>Featured SCP!</p> </div> <div class="panel-body"> <h2><span><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1039">SCP-1039</a>: The Gathering Doll</span></h2> <p><em>The head of SCP-1039 has been known to turn towards agents within the containment cell, independent of the body, as if staring at them.</em></p> </div> <div class="panel-footer"> <p>Featured SCP.</p> </div> </div> <div class="content-panel right-column"> <div class="panel-heading"> <p>Featured Tale/Format!</p> </div> <div class="panel-body"> <h2><span><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/supply-and-demand">Supply and Demand</a></span></h2> <p><em>His heart leapt and he felt the hold on his body disappear. Karsten turned, only to be left staring at a hollow, fire-blackened skull.</em><br /></p> </div> <div class="panel-footer"> <p>Featured non-SCP.</p> </div> </div> <br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span> <hr /> <div style="text-align: center;"> <h1><span>Topic and Prompt of the month!</span></h1> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsi